snippet.title: Dune: Awakening - Unreal Engine 5.2 Trailer | State of Unreal 2024
snippet.description: Joel Bylos, creative director of Dune: Awakening by Funcom, presents the visuals of the game's landscape and models inspired by the visual effects of Dune 2, which used Unreal Engine 5 in the film. And he treated audiences to the teaser trailer.
